cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new method for supervised sequence modeling using recurrent neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and can be applied to various tasks such as action recognition (cs.CV), sentiment analysis (cs.CL), and natural language processing (cs.AI). The method involves non-local operations and global interactions, which are also relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
